eutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">587BLK/BLK</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Black with Black Ink</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">587BLK/BLUE</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Black with Blue Ink</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">587DKBLUE/BLK</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Dark Blue with Black Ink</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">587DKBLUE/BLUE</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Dark Blue with Blue Ink</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">587DKGRN/BLK</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Dark Green with Black Ink</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">587DKGRN/BLUE</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Dark Green with Blue Ink</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">587GRAY/BLK</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Light Gray with Black Ink</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">587GRAY/BLUE</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Light Gray with Blue Ink</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">587RED/BLK</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Red with Black Ink</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">587RED/BLUE</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Red with Blue Ink</p></div></div>\n</details>\n</div>\n</div>\n<h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-700 mt-5 mb-2\">Standard decoration (included)</h4>\n<p class=\"text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">1 Color, 1 Location</p>\n<h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-700 mt-5 mb-2\">All available decoration options</h4>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-[13px] leading-snug\"><li>Silk Screen: 1.63&quot; W x 0.5&quot; H Barrel</li><li>Tip Type: Ballpoint</li><li>Mechanism: Push Retractable</li><li>Click Here For Virtual Proofing Tool</li></ul>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500 mt-4\">Final quote may reflect selected options, proofs, rush, or freight beyond list pricing.</p>\n</div>","salesToolsHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p><strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">Pitch this SKU</strong> — MaxGlide® Click Corporate Pen (Pat #D709,950). Lead with use case (uniforms, retail, teams, recognition), then minimums and timeline. Reference included services from “Price includes” in the Description tab when present (e.g. setup, virtual proof, shipping offers).</p>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-2\">\n<li>Quote style <span class=\"font-mono text-neutral-900\">587</span> on proposals and POs.</li>\n<li>Offer virtual proofs and artwork checks before production.</li>\n<li>Cross-sell with hats, bags, or jackets for kit programs.</li>\n<li>For decoration and imprint methods, follow supplier notes in the Description tab.</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500\">Approved partners can request internal sell sheets, comparison matrices, and margin guidance from the A Design Line team.</p>\n</div>","inventoryHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p>Merchandise is <strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">typically sourced to order</strong>. Stock and availability may vary by supplier and season.</p>\n<p>Supplier-stated production window: <strong>5 days</strong> (not including transit).</p>\n<p>Contact the studio for <strong>rush</strong> feasibility, <strong>split shipments</strong>, or <strong>multi-location</strong> drops before placing large orders.</p>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500\">Minimum order quantity: <strong class=\"text-neutral-800\">250</strong> units (per catalog line).</p>\n</div>"}